'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 44''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 44''',  was the 44th issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]''. It was released on [[April 17]], [[2003]] and reprinted content from [[Star Wars Insider 64|''Star Wars Insider'' 64]] and earlier issues.

==Contents==
===Departments===
*[[Feel the Force]]
*[[Prequel Update]]
*New Hopes
*[[Jawa's Corner]]
**[[Bookshelf]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 64}}
**[[Comics Link]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 64}}
**[[Gamescape]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 63}}
*[[Set Piece]] &mdash; Theed Palace Hangar {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 60}}
*[[Star Wars Q&A|''Star Wars'' Q&A]]
*[[Comlink (department)|Comlink]]

===Features===
*"Inside Episode II: Unlocking the Camera"
*:<small>Discover how the digital world is matched to the real world in this behind-the-scenes story from the making of Episode II.</small>
*"[[Feedback Loop: Ben Burtt in 30 Years of Star Wars Sounds|Feedback Loop: Ben Burtt in 30 Years of ''Star Wars' Sounds]]" {{C|[[Star Wars Insider 64|''Star Wars Insider'' 64]]}}
*"[[Dream Weavers: The People of Industrial Light & Magic]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 64}}
*"[[Return to Endor: The Stars of the Ewok Films Remember Their Adventure]]" {{C|[[Star Wars Insider 62|''Star Wars Insider'' 62]]}}
*"''Star Wars'' Roleplaying Game Books"
*:<small>An in-depth look at two new volumes for the ''Star Wars'' Roleplaying Game which allow you to bring the Force to life in your own home...</small>

